4:["$","section",null,{"className":"container mx-auto px-6 py-12 max-w-4xl text-center","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed","children":["Learning to drive in ","Brighton","? UNO Driving School offers professional automatic driving lessons tailored to your skill level. Our patient instructors focus on building safe, confident drivers, helping students pass their Queensland driving test on the first go."]}]}]
5:["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-blue-50 py-14","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-anton text-3xl uppercase mb-6 text-text-main text-center","children":["Local Roads and Driving Conditions in ","Brighton"]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 mb-10 text-center mx-auto","children":[["$","p","0",{"children":"Looking for driving lessons in Brighton? UNO Driving School provides calm, automatic driving lessons for learners across Brighton, Sandgate, Deagon and Bracken Ridge. Our 5-star instructors help Brighton students pass their Queensland driving test on the first attempt."}],["$","p","1",{"children":"Brighton dominates the northernmost tip of the Brisbane coastal peninsula, adjacent to the Hornibrook Bridge. The driving landscape here is highly varied, ranging from the incredibly long, flat, straight coastal esplanade to the dense internal grid of post-war residential streets. The internal grids are exceptionally quiet, making Brighton a magnificent, safe starting point for absolute beginners."}],["$","p","2",{"children":"As the student outgrows the safety of the backstreets, our instructors use Beaconsfield Terrace and the approaches to the Hornibrook Bridge to introduce high-speed merging and continuous multi-lane management. This progression from absolute calm to highway-style arterials guarantees that Brighton students are deeply prepared for their TMR test at Carseldine or Zillmere."}],["$","p","3",{"children":"Brighton learners frequently test at the Carseldine TMR Customer Service Centre. Free pickup from Brighton, modern automatic vehicles, Afterpay available. Book today."}]]}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-blue-100 flex items-start gap-4","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-primary text-xl mt-0.5","children":"